Cyber Claw:







Cyber Claw spat at the other raptor. He bobbed her head, furious. The other 
hadn't tooken her warning.

"You are the coward!" Her voice had turned fully into Dinobot's tone. "You 
are in my terriotry! Get out!" She was afraid now, and angry at the same 
time. Was it a good idea to say this was her terriotry? If this other female 
knew it now, she could tell Megatron, and it would be turning tail time 
again. "Get out of her before I rip you to shreds!"
